here was plenty to quibble with in the event - and especially its coverage on NBC - whether it was the decapitated Marie Antoinettes, the book-nerd threesome, the foggy camera lenses, or the glaring lack of context or insight from the network's commentators.\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 711, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 531, \"end\": 534, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9999999997176019, \"rank\": 2.1991969033852722e-10, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Whatever one's cultural or political perspective\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 450}, {\"ngram\": \"plenty\", \"from\": 462, \"to\": 468}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 488, \"to\": 497}, {\"ngram\": \"the decapitated Marie Antoinettes\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 585}, {\"ngram\": \"the book-nerd threesome\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 610}, {\"ngram\": \"the foggy camera lenses\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 635}, {\"ngram\": \"the glaring lack\", \"from\": 640, \"to\": 656}, {\"ngram\": \"context\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 667}, {\"ngram\": \"insight\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 678}, {\"ngram\": \"the network's commentators\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 710}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But conservatives in the United States - and elsewhere - are upset over a portion of the ceremony that wasn't even broadcast in its entirety on NBC.\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 861, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 738, \"end\": 751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999994509090955, \"rank\": 5.490909243213634e-07, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 857, \"end\": 860, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9999999997176019, \"rank\": 2.1991969033852722e-10, \"text\