 2373}, {\"ngram\": \"no bounds\", \"from\": 2380, \"to\": 2389}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But we know that truth and virtue will always prevail.\\\"\", \"from\": 2397, \"to\": 2452, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"truth\", \"from\": 2414, \"to\": 2419}, {\"ngram\": \"virtue\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2430}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Never one to let a culture war skirmish pass her by, Rep. Marjorie Taylor Greene (R-Ga.) also weighed in, denouncing the ceremony as \\\"anti-Christian\\\" and \\\"satanic, trans and occult.\\\"\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2635, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2511, \"end\": 2533, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marjorie_Taylor_Greene\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marjorie Taylor Greene\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marjorie_Taylor_Greene\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marjorie_Taylor_Greene\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a culture war\", \"from\": 2470, \"to\": 2483}, {\"ngram\": \"R-Ga.\", \"from\": 2535, \"to\": 2540}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 2570, \"to\": 2582}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"satanic, trans\", \"from\": 2607, \"to\": 2622}, {\"ngram\": \"occult\", \"from\": 2627, \"to\": 2633}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even \\\"Full House\\\" star Candace Cameron Bure gave her two cents - and then some - on Instagram.\", \"from\": 2636, \"to\": 2730, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2659, \"end\": 2679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Candace Cameron Bure\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\"}, {\"begin\": 2675, \"end\": 2679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/River_Bure\", \"score\": 0.9673856842746074, \"rank\": 0.033713870543512575, \"text\": \"Bure\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q40