y artistic choices\", \"from\": 4164, \"to\": 4183}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a statement from her lawyer, Butch said she had been \\\"threatened with death, torture and rape,\\\" and been the target of \\\"anti-Semitic, homophobic, sexist and grossophobic insults,\\\" and was filing complaints against her detractors.\", \"from\": 4186, \"to\": 4418, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4309, \"end\": 4321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antisemitism\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1663861079566258e-19, \"text\": \"anti-Semitic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antisemitism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antisemitism\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 4189, \"to\": 4200}, {\"ngram\": \"her lawyer\", \"from\": 4206, \"to\": 4216}, {\"ngram\": \"Butch\", \"from\": 4218, \"to\": 4223}, {\"ngram\": \"death\", \"from\": 4259, \"to\": 4264}, {\"ngram\": \"torture\", \"from\": 4266, \"to\": 4273}, {\"ngram\": \"rape\", \"from\": 4278, \"to\": 4282}, {\"ngram\": \"the target\", \"from\": 4294, \"to\": 4304}, {\"ngram\": \"complaints\", \"from\": 4384, \"to\": 4394}, {\"ngram\": \"her detractors\", \"from\": 4403, \"to\": 4417}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thomas Jolly, the artistic director of the opening ceremony, has denied that \\\"The Last Supper\\\" inspired the tableau, or that he intended to belittle anyone's beliefs.\", \"from\": 4420, \"to\": 4586, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4420, \"end\": 4426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"score\": 0.9999990763708129, \"rank\": 9.000451241021915e-07, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the artistic director\", \"from\": 4434, \"to\": 4455}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 4459, \"to\": 4479}, {\"ngram\": \"The Last Supper\", \"from\": 4498, \"to\": 4513}, {\"ngram\": \"the tableau\", \"from\": 4524, \"to\": 4535}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone's beliefs\", \"from\": 4569, \"to\": 4585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The idea was to create a big pagan party ... you will never find in me, or in my work, any desire of mocking anyone,\\\" he said in an interview with the French broadcast network BFMTV.\", \"from\": 4587, \"to\": 4770, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4739, \"end\": 4745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9996911083846699, \"rank\": 0.00016193606101696424, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 4764, \"end\": 4769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BFMTV\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The idea\", \"from\": 4588, \"to\": 4596}, {\"ngram\": \"a big pagan party\", \"from\": 4611, \"to\": 4628}, {\"ngram\": \"my work\", \"from\": 4666, \"to\": 4673}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 4697, \"to\": 4703}, {\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 4717, \"to\": 4729}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jolly did not elaborate about his inspiration, but someart experts see more similarities with paintingslike \\\"The Feast of the Gods,\\\" by Jan van Bijlert.\", \"from\": 4772, \"to\": 4924, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4908, \"end\": 4923, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jan_van_Bijlert\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jan van Bijlert\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jan_van_Bijlert\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jan_van_Bijlert\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his inspiration\", \"from\": 4802, \"to\": 4817}, {\"ngram\": \"someart experts\", \"from\": 4823, \"to\": 4838}, {\"ngram\": \"more similarities\", \"from\": 4843, \"to\": 4860}, {\"ngram\": \"paintingslike \\\"The Feast\", \"from\": 4866, \"to\": 4890}, {\"ngram\": \"the Gods\", \"from\": 4894, \"to\": 4902}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The conservative outrage also fails to make a distinction between a work of art painted more than 1,400 years after Jesus' crucifixion - one that is celebrated as much for its brilliant composition and use of perspective as for its religious message - and the New Testament accounts of the final meal Jesus shared with his apostles.\", \"from\": 4926, \"to\": 5258, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5042, \"end\": 5047, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.7421531176800856e-13, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}, {\"begin\": 5186, \"end\": 5199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Testament\", \"score\": 0.9993962877091447, \"rank\": 0.0006040769793930846, \"text\": \"New Testament\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Testament\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Testament\"}, {\"begin\": 5227, \"end\": 5232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.7421531176800856e-13, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The conservative outrage\", \"from\": 4926, \"to\": 4950}, {\"ngram\": \"a distinction\", \"from\": 4970, \"to\": 4983}, {\"ngram\": \"a work\", \"from\": 4992, \"to\": 4998}, {\"ngram\": \"art\", \"from\": 5002, \"to\": 5005}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 1,400 years\", \"from\": 5014, \"to\": 5035}, {\"ngram\":